(1, 'The Secret Power of Brands', 'Understand the role of brands and brand management in the modern world, and start developing your career in the sector.', 'Brands are the most potent commercial and cultural force on the planet. Think about McDonaldâs, Apple, Manchester United, Tate, Google or even Harry Potter. This free online course will help you get under the skin of such brands, and ask how and why they become so powerful.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-secret-power-of-brands', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2958812.mp4', '2015-11-02', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ce/b8/regular_ceb87398-86f6-4633-b705-cd4ddff00223.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:00:05'),
(2, 'The Mind is Flat: the Shocking Shallowness of Human Psychology', 'Make better personal and professional decisions, considering the psychological dimension to choices, with this free online course.', 'What are the forces shaping human behaviour? How do we think and decide? This course, from Professor Nick Chater and Warwick Business School, explores the origins of human rationality and irrationality.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-mind-is-flat', '', '2015-11-09', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/12/3e/regular_123ecc58-cdac-4e5f-84b0-64a2964fcfdf.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Warwick', '2015-11-04 00:00:06'),
(3, 'Contract Management: Building Relationships in Business', 'Learn to build relationships and manage contracts successfully with this free online course backed by UK government and IACCM.', 'Contracts are fundamental to all business activities and relationships are fundamental to all contracts.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/contract-management', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2948275.mp4', '2015-11-09', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9c/20/regular_9c2020d8-f89d-4033-893a-6fbd365fac4b.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:00:06'),
(4, 'Intercultural Communication', 'Learn to appreciate, adjust to, and work or study in different cultures, with this free online intercultural communication course.', 'Whether youâre engaging in business across borders or cultural regions, meeting other people through international travel, working in a diverse, global organisation or studying abroad, you can benefit from a better understanding of intercultural communication.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/intercultural-communication', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5346186.mp4', '2015-11-09', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/73/7e/regular_737e6fa1-bed3-4711-b089-cc21677a10e8.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Shanghai International Studies University (SISU)', '2015-11-04 00:00:07'),
(5, 'Developing Cultural Intelligence for Leadership', 'Find out what Cultural Intelligence (CQ) is, and why good leaders and managers need it, in this free online course.', 'Cultural Intelligence (CQ) is the natural evolution from the well-established notions of IQ (intelligence quotient) and EQ (emotional intelligence). Good leaders need all three to lead effectively.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/cultural-intelligence', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4735645.mp4', '2015-11-09', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/db/f4/regular_dbf4d500-c8cd-4df9-b921-02d96132c009.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Common Purpose', '2015-11-04 00:00:08'),
(6, 'How to Succeed at: Interviews', 'This free three week course provides the tools you need to succeed at interviews and land your dream job or course place.', 'This course will help you to succeed at interviews, whether you are applying for jobs or planning to study. Because being offered an interview can be quite daunting, weâve put together a set of materials to help you prepare and be successful on the day.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/interviews', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3030237.mp4', '2015-11-16', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e1/6a/regular_e16aaa55-5f57-43f6-801f-cccc179f1e21.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:00:09'),
(7, 'The Internet of Things', 'Learn how IoT works, and how to create a successful product or company using it, with this free online course.', 'Entrepreneurs love it, large corporations love it, universities and now even governments love it â welcome to the exciting and emerging world of the Internet of Things (IoT).', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/internet-of-things', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4611259.mp4', '2015-11-23', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8e/44/regular_8e442a5c-4cee-4fd3-8f8f-ed04df2789cd.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Kings College London', '2015-11-04 00:00:09'),
(8, 'Managing My Investments', 'Gain the skills to manage your investments: analyse portfolio risk and plan your pension, with this free online course.', 'Research shows that UK households are poor at investment management with a limited understanding of investment choices, risks and returns. The resultant âsavings gapâ threatens a scenario where many cannot afford to retire.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/managing-my-investments', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2770520.mp4', '2016-01-04', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/bc/02/regular_bc025666-072c-4378-9cf1-3bab52b6d7dc.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:00:10'),
(9, 'Supply Chain Innovation: How Technology Can Create a Sustainable Future', 'Understand how new technologies can make supply chains more sustainable and learn how to deal with todays trends.', 'Every product that we use today is the result of a supply chain - a complex series of steps that turn raw materials into the final products we use and everything related with this. Managing these supply chains has become more and more a challenge, especially with all modern technologies and todays trends. The 24-hour economy, fast delivery of goods to your home, wanting to have customized products and of course the focus on sustainability are a few of these trends.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/supply-chain-innovation', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5282692.mp4', '2016-01-11', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/c3/5f/regular_c35fa072-a305-4a64-8787-1529c1e13589.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Twente', '2015-11-04 00:00:11'),
(10, 'Behind the Scenes at the 21st Century Museum', 'Get an introduction to museum studies with this free online course. Learn about the people and ideas that shape museums today', 'How can we understand museums today? Who are museums for and why are they working to engage new audiences? How do we respond emotionally to museum objects and spaces? And how can museums play a role in the pursuit of social justice, human rights, or health and wellbeing?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/museum', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2656218.mp4', '2016-01-18', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/93/8b/regular_938bf370-e957-4471-b498-ea6fc66d3625.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leicester', '2015-11-04 00:00:12'),
(11, 'How to Build a Sustainable Fashion Business', 'Learn from leading entrepreneurs what it takes to create a successful fashion business, with a social or environmental ethos.', 'Weâre the Ethical Fashion Forum, the global industry body for sustainable fashion. Since 2006, weâve been helping fashion professionals achieve commercial success, while maximising benefits to communities and minimising negative environmental impacts.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/sustainable-fashion', '', '2016-01-18', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/77/74/regular_7774142d-b953-47a4-b242-48414fcf9089.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Creative Skillset', '2015-11-04 00:00:12'),
(12, 'Understanding Public Financial Management: How Is Your Money Spent?', 'How do governments acquire and spend public money? Take a fresh look at public financial management with this free online course.', 'What went wrong in Greeceâs handling of its public debt? How does a city government like Detroit go from prosperity to bankruptcy? And how could the looting, theft and corruption in Malawiâs âcashgateâ have been avoided?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/public-financial-management', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5441427.mp4', '2016-01-25', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ef/12/regular_ef1250d1-3017-48da-b50d-d032a15e5029.jpg', 'Business & Management', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'SOAS, University of London', '2015-11-04 00:00:14'),
